Create inline icon links.

=== Example Usage ===
<pre><nowiki>* Please visit {{Inline icon link|image=Vrrat_thumbsup.png|link=https://vrchat.com|desc=the home of VRRat!|size=20px|caption=VRRat thinks you're cool}}!</nowiki></pre>

will make:

* Please visit {{Inline icon link|image=Vrrat_thumbsup.png|link=https://vrchat.com|desc=the home of VRRat!|size=20px|caption=VRRat thinks you're cool}}!

